rows.name:
I want to send Shenka to visit
Gula someday so she can try
the confections there.

rows.label: tlk45400251_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently Superbian cuisine
is not very well-regarded
by the global community.

rows.label: tlk45400251_03_msg0003
rows.name:
So I want to give Shenka the opportunity
to try Gulan cuisine, which is
supposed to be quite delicious.

rows.label: tlk45400251_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm sure it would help her
to improve her own recipes.
